    "body": "you can simply use a function internal to what you do. Even if I agreed that this should be changed, this would take a month or more to make it to the next release, then you would have to update, etc.\n\n```\ndef read_hdf(fname, key, mode=None, **kwargs):\n    if mode is None:\n         mode = 'r'\n    return pd.read_hdf(fname, key, mode=mode, **kwargs)\n```\n"
